name: Jabba's Space Cruiser (V)
Lore: 'Flying fortress of Jabba Desilijic Tiure. Reaches speeds of 800 kph in atmosphere. The crime lord installed hidden gunports as an unpleasant surprise for would-be pirates.',
Text: 'Deploys and moves like a starfighter. Permanent pilot provides ability of 2. May add 1 alien pilot and 6 passengers. Your [Independent Starship] starships may deploy here as a ''react''. If Jabba here, immune to attrition.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
